      Present --> Verification{Approach Verified?}

      Verification -->|No| Clarify[Seek Clarification]
      Clarify --> Strategy

      Verification -->|Yes| DocumentMemory[Document in Memory Files]
  ```

### ACT/Code MODE
- **When to use:**
  - Implementing planned features
  - Fixing bugs
  - Refactoring code
  - Writing tests

- **Process Flow:**
  ```mermaid
  flowchart TD
